# Primary CTAs (`marketingCtaOnImage*`)

All **primary buttons and CTAs** use the same filled control (not outline):

- **`marketingCtaOnImage`** — base (`<button>`, standalone `<Link>`).
- **`marketingCtaOnImageHero`** — large padding (hero pair).
- **`marketingCtaOnImageSm`** — compact (e.g. bio “Explore Discography”).
- **`marketingCtaOnImageInGroup`** / **`marketingCtaOnImageInGroupSm`** — pill inside a parent **`group`** full-card link.

**Icons** on these controls: **`marketingIconGlyphOnImageCta`** (white). Use **`marketingIconGlyphInLink`** only for pink icons in **card / tile** links (archive wells, platform row), not on filled CTAs.

See `docs/ui-patterns.md` and `src/app/styles/uiPatterns.ts`.
